msgid "Too many attempts. Please wait a few minutes and try again."
msgstr ""
"Terlalu banyak percobaan. Silakan tunggu beberapa menit dan coba lagi."

msgid "Buyer — browse products, contact sellers and post comments"
msgstr "Pembeli — jelajahi produk, hubungi penjual, dan tulis komentar"

msgid "Seller — list and manage products for sale"
msgstr "Penjual — mendaftarkan dan mengelola produk untuk dijual"

msgid "Buyer & Seller — everything in one account"
msgstr "Pembeli & Penjual — semuanya dalam satu akun"

msgid "Password changed"
msgstr "Kata sandi telah diubah"

msgid ""
"Your password has been set. You can now sign in with your new password."
msgstr ""
"Kata sandi Anda telah diatur. Anda sekarang bisa masuk dengan kata sandi "
"baru."

msgid "Sign in"
msgstr "Masuk"

msgid "Choose a new password"
msgstr "Pilih kata sandi baru"

msgid "Set new password"
msgstr "Atur kata sandi baru"

msgid ""
"This password reset link is invalid or has expired. Please request a new "
"one."
msgstr ""
"Tautan reset kata sandi ini tidak valid atau sudah kedaluwarsa. Silakan "
"minta yang baru."

msgid "Request a new link"
msgstr "Minta tautan baru"

msgid "Reset link sent"
msgstr "Tautan reset telah dikirim"

msgid "Check your email"
msgstr "Periksa email Anda"

msgid ""
"If an account exists with the address you entered, we have emailed a "
"password reset link."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada akun dengan alamat yang Anda masukkan, kami telah mengirimkan "
"tautan reset kata sandi melalui email."

msgid "Back to sign in"
msgstr "Kembali ke halaman masuk"

msgid ""
"You are receiving this email because you requested a password reset for your"
" TimorMart account."
msgstr ""
"Anda menerima email ini karena Anda meminta reset kata sandi untuk akun "
"TimorMart Anda."

msgid "Please go to the following page and choose a new password:"
msgstr "Silakan kunjungi halaman berikut dan pilih kata sandi baru:"

msgid "Your username, in case you have forgotten:"
msgstr "Nama pengguna Anda, jika Anda lupa:"

msgid "If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak meminta ini, Anda bisa mengabaikan email ini dengan aman."

msgid "Reset password"
msgstr "Reset kata sandi"

msgid "Reset your password"
msgstr "Reset kata sandi Anda"

msgid ""
"Enter the email address you registered with and we will send you a link to "
"set a new password."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan alamat email yang Anda gunakan saat mendaftar dan kami akan "
"mengirimkan tautan untuk mengatur kata sandi baru."

msgid "Send reset link"
msgstr "Kirim tautan reset"

msgid "Sign up"
msgstr "Daftar"

msgid "Create an account"
msgstr "Buat akun"

msgid "Already have an account?"
msgstr "Sudah punya akun?"

#, python-format
msgid "Welcome, %(name)s! Your account is ready — happy shopping."
msgstr "Selamat datang, %(name)s! Akun Anda sudah siap — selamat berbelanja."

#, python-format
msgid "Welcome, %(name)s! Your seller account is ready."
msgstr "Selamat datang, %(name)s! Akun penjual Anda sudah siap."

msgid "Please correct the errors below."
msgstr "Silakan perbaiki kesalahan di bawah ini."

#, python-format
msgid "Welcome back, %(name)s!"
msgstr "Selamat datang kembali, %(name)s!"

msgid "Invalid username or password."
msgstr "Nama pengguna atau kata sandi tidak valid."

msgid "You have been logged out."
msgstr "Anda telah keluar."

msgid ""
"Administrator accounts manage the platform and cannot buy or sell products."
msgstr ""
"Akun administrator mengelola platform dan tidak dapat membeli atau menjual "
"produk."

msgid "Your account already has the buyer role."
msgstr "Akun Anda sudah memiliki peran pembeli."

msgid ""
"Your account is now Buyer & Seller — you can contact sellers and post "
"comments."
msgstr ""
"Akun Anda sekarang Pembeli & Penjual — Anda dapat menghubungi penjual dan "
"menulis komentar."

